"title": "8300: love, and the world",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8300: love, and the world",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture promotes the love of family, home and country and contains many examples of such love.</p>\n<h2>Parental love</h2>\n<h3>Aspects of parental love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:24\">PRO 13:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:4\">EPH 6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:7\">DEU 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:14\">2CO 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:21\">COL 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:4\">1TI 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of maternal love</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:16\">GEN 21:16</a> <em>Hagar</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:3\">EXO 2:3</a> <em>Moses' mother</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:28\">JDG 5:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:19\">1SA 2:19</a> <em>Hannah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:10\">2SA 21:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:26\">1KI 3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:18\">1KI 17:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:20\">2KI 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:27\">2KI 4:27</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:22\">MAT 15:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:26\">MRK 7:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:48\">LUK 2:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:12-Luke7:13\">LUK 7:12–7:13</a> <em>the widow of Nain</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:25\">JHN 19:25</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of paternal love</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:2\">GEN 22:2</a> <em>Abraham</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:28\">GEN 31:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:35\">GEN 37:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:38\">GEN 42:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:16\">2SA 12:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:39\">2SA 13:39</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:23\">MRK 5:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:41-Luke8:42\">LUK 8:41–8:42</a> <em>Jairus</em></p>\n<h2>Love for parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen46:29\">GEN 46:29</a> <em>Joseph</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:3\">LEV 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:36\">JDG 11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:3\">1SA 22:3</a> <em>David</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:20\">1KI 19:20</a> <em>Elisha</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:8\">JER 35:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:4\">MAT 15:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:10\">MRK 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:51\">LUK 2:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:26-John19:27\">JHN 19:26–19:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1\">EPH 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20\">COL 3:20</a></p>\n<h2>Other instances of family love</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:7\">GEN 34:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:14-Gen45:15\">GEN 45:14–45:15</a> <em>Joseph and his brothers</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:16-Ruth1:17\">RUT 1:16–1:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:22\">2SA 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:7\">EST 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:11\">EST 2:11</a></p>\n<h2>Love of home and country</h2>\n<h3>Examples of love of home</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:30\">GEN 31:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:29\">GEN 49:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:25\">GEN 50:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:30\">NUM 10:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:6\">RUT 1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:12\">2SA 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:37\">2SA 19:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:15\">2SA 23:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:14\">NEH 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Exhortations to patriotism</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:6\">PSA 122:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:5-Ps137:6\">PSA 137:5–137:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:20\">2SA 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:8\">EST 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:50\">JER 51:50</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of patriotism</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:26\">1SA 17:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam27:8-1Sam27:10\">1SA 27:8–27:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:3-Neh1:4\">NEH 1:3–1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:5\">NEH 2:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:6\">EST 8:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:1\">PSA 137:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:51\">JER 51:51</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:3\">ROM 9:3</a></p>",
